title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Hanuman vs. 7 Ultraman
itunes:title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Hanuman vs. 7 Ultraman
description:
In this episode of Weirdhouse Cinema, Rob and Joe consider the 1974 Thai co-production "Hanuman vs. & Ultraman," in which the hindu god Hanuman teams up with the Ultra Seven to defeat evil monsters and dastardly human plots.
